---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Disclaimer from '../components/Disclaimer.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
	title="About Antonio Rodríguez Martínez"
	description="Systems builder. Warrior poet. Father. I write, build, and create with integrity."
	pubDate={new Date('May 01 2025')}
	language={['en']}
	category={['about']}
	robots={{
		index: true,
		follow: true,
		noarchive: false,
		nosnippet: false,
		noimageindex: false
	}}
	layoutType="blog"
>

	<p>
		I build systems — digital, emotional, spiritual, and physical.
	</p>

	<p>
		I'm a technical program manager, software architect, and developer with over a decade of experience building scalable products. I've founded companies, led teams, and shipped software used by millions. Now I split my time between building tools, raising my kids, and building a homestead in Puerto Rico.
	</p>

	<p>
		But that's just part of it.
	</p>

	<p>
		I'm also a father, artist, martial artist, mentor, and the founder of <strong>Strong Hands, Soft Heart</strong> — a brand devoted to practical strength, emotional depth, and sacred self-reliance.
	</p>

	<p>
		This blog is where I document it all:
	</p>

	<ul>
		<li><strong>Art & Expression</strong> 🎵 — creative soul, aesthetic power, truth-telling</li>
		<li><strong>DIY & Creation</strong> 🛠️ — physical builds, handmade goods, crafting</li>
		<li><strong>Integration & Growth</strong> 🧘🏽‍♂️ — inner mastery, parenting, masculine leadership</li>
		<li><strong>Learning Projects</strong> 📚 — documentation of mastery in progress</li>
		<li><strong>Metaspace</strong> 🌀 — reflections on the journey itself</li>
		<li><strong>Parenting</strong> 👨‍👩‍👧‍👦 — raising resilient children, family dynamics, and personal growth</li>
		<li><strong>Politics</strong> ⚖️ — power dynamics, social structures, and collective healing</li>
		<li><strong>Psychology</strong> 🧠 — human behavior, social dynamics, and mental processes</li>
		<li><strong>Systems & Strategy</strong> 💻 — technical systems, organizational design, and strategic thinking</li>
	</ul>

	<p>
		Join me on this journey of exploration, creation, and growth.
	</p>

	<h2>👇 Links</h2>
	<ul>
		<li>🛠 <a href="https://builds.software">Builds.software</a> — my technical portfolio</li>
		<li>💜 <a href="https://stronghandssoftheart.com">Strong Hands, Soft Heart</a> — my brand</li>
		<li>🐙 <a href="https://github.com/antoniwan">GitHub</a> — open source & code</li>
		<li>🌀 <a href="https://bsky.app/profile/antoniwan.online">BlueSky</a> — my social brain</li>
	</ul>

	<p>
		If you're building something good, or trying to become someone better,<br />
		I'm probably down to help.<br />
		Get in touch.
	</p>

	<Disclaimer />
</BaseLayout>

